[30;1m30 | [0m[35m    Because the order in which individual write operations are applied to the database[0m
[30;1m31 | [0m[35m    is not guaranteed, `batch_write` RPCs can never contain multiple operations[0m

[30;1m33 | [0m[35m    known document reference, it should first cut off the previous batch and[0m
[30;1m34 | [0m[35m    send it, then create a new batch starting with the latest write operation.[0m
